societies, the Turin Shroud,

00:03:09.890 --> 00:03:12.190 align:middle line:84%
and even the Holy Grail
would find their way

00:03:12.190 --> 00:03:14.615 align:middle line:84%
into the folklore of
the Knights Templar.

00:03:14.615 --> 00:03:17.730 align:middle line:90%


00:03:17.730 --> 00:03:21.690 align:middle line:84%
Could any of these fantastic
rumors possibly be true?

00:03:21.690 --> 00:03:24.920 align:middle line:84%
