their amazing secrets

00:03:24.920 --> 00:03:26.370 align:middle line:90%
for the last 700 years?

00:03:26.370 --> 00:03:42.750 align:middle line:90%


00:03:42.750 --> 00:03:46.630 align:middle line:10%
>>Pope Urban II
called what we now

00:03:46.630 --> 00:03:50.010 align:middle line:10%
describe as a crusade in 1096.

00:03:50.010 --> 00:03:52.800 align:middle line:84%
