East, having fulfilled

00:04:08.190 --> 00:04:11.910 align:middle line:84%
their Crusades vows, and
returned to the West.

00:04:11.910 --> 00:04:14.750 align:middle line:84%
And the Crusaders were left--
the crusade settlers were

00:04:14.750 --> 00:04:19.760 align:middle line:84%
left with very little
in the way of defenses.

00:04:19.760 --> 00:04:22.070 align:middle line:84%
