really, the Templars

00:04:33.670 --> 00:04:37.220 align:middle line:84%
were founded by a group
of Western knights,

00:04:37.220 --> 00:04:40.320 align:middle line:84%
French knights, who were
living in the East, who

00:04:40.320 --> 00:04:44.180 align:middle line:84%
wanted to engage
in a charitable act

00:04:44.180 --> 00:04:49.930 align:middle line:84%
and perhaps also ensure their
own salvation by defending

00:04:49.930 --> 00:04:53.170 align:middle line:84%
and protecting these
groups of pilgrims

00:04:53.170 --> 00:04:55.360 align:middle line:90%
who went to see the holy places.

00:04:55.360 --> 00:05:00.335 align:middle line:84%
