00:14:33.500 --> 00:14:34.220 align:middle line:90%
over generations.

00:14:34.220 --> 00:14:38.180 align:middle line:90%


00:14:38.180 --> 00:14:41.800 align:middle line:10%
>>The cavalry charge
was their-- effectively

00:14:41.800 --> 00:14:45.140 align:middle line:10%
