00:15:12.220 --> 00:15:19.920 align:middle line:90%


00:15:19.920 --> 00:15:22.590 align:middle line:84%
>>The Templar's famous
turcopoles were former Muslims

00:15:22.590 --> 00:15:25.570 align:middle line:84%
