00:15:25.570 --> 00:15:27.400 align:middle line:84%
and who, like the
Templars themselves,

00:15:27.400 --> 00:15:29.525 align:middle line:84%
could be counted on
to fight to the death,

00:15:29.525 --> 00:15:32.010 align:middle line:84%
as they also faced
immediate execution if they

00:15:32.010 --> 00:15:32.958 align:middle line:90%
