00:15:32.958 --> 00:15:40.350 align:middle line:90%


00:15:40.350 --> 00:15:42.780 align:middle line:84%
Horses were vital
to the Crusaders,

00:15:42.780 --> 00:15:46.670 align:middle line:84%
