00:18:49.520 --> 00:18:54.635 align:middle line:84%
the faults of the Jordan, were
not protected by the Franks.

00:18:54.635 --> 00:19:05.930 align:middle line:84%
In 1178, a year after
a very decisive victory

00:19:05.930 --> 00:19:10.540 align:middle line:84%
