territory which was considered

00:19:28.270 --> 00:19:32.035 align:middle line:84%
by both Franks and Muslims
as a Muslim territory.

00:19:32.035 --> 00:19:38.370 align:middle line:90%


00:19:38.370 --> 00:19:40.880 align:middle line:84%
>>The Templars' newly
built castle on the Jordan

00:19:40.880 --> 00:19:43.660 align:middle line:84%
was in just too important
a location for Saladin

00:19:43.660 --> 00:19:45.320 align:middle line:90%
