stake, the Templars

00:20:03.500 --> 00:20:06.160 align:middle line:84%
had no choice but to abandon
their policy of caution.

00:20:06.160 --> 00:20:10.370 align:middle line:90%


00:20:10.370 --> 00:20:12.220 align:middle line:84%
