00:20:19.906 --> 00:20:23.260 align:middle line:90%


00:20:23.260 --> 00:20:26.260 align:middle line:84%
Saladin's first great invasion
of the Christian state

00:20:26.260 --> 00:20:28.190 align:middle line:90%
came not long afterwards.

00:20:28.190 --> 00:20:30.760 align:middle line:84%
The Templars once more
put their faith in God

00:20:30.760 --> 00:20:32.660 align:middle line:84%
and launched their
heavy cavalry charge

00:20:32.660 --> 00:20:35.400 align:middle line:84%
against a numerically
superior enemy.

00:20:35.400 --> 00:20:37.980 align:middle line:84%
The charge caught the
Muslim forces by surprise

00:20:37.980 --> 00:20:39.550 align:middle line:90%
and inflicted a crushing defeat.

00:20:39.550 --> 00:20:42.780 align:middle line:90%


00:20:42.780 --> 00:20:45.650 align:middle line:84%
The Templars deployed
the same proven tactics

00:20:45.650 --> 00:20:48.360 align:middle line:84%
a few years later
in 1187, when they

00:20:48.360 --> 00:20:51.700 align:middle line:84%
