00:21:03.730 --> 00:21:05.190 align:middle line:90%
their size.

00:21:05.190 --> 00:21:08.120 align:middle line:90%
This time, the cavalry failed.

00:21:08.120 --> 00:21:10.750 align:middle line:84%
60 Templar Knights
