00:21:53.200 --> 00:21:59.180 align:middle line:84%
Some Christians felt that
Templar pride must be to blame.

00:21:59.180 --> 00:22:02.370 align:middle line:84%
What the Templars saw as
a noble collective spirit

00:22:02.370 --> 00:22:04.840 align:middle line:84%
