many, including the Templar

00:23:09.550 --> 00:23:12.670 align:middle line:84%
grandmaster, they decided
to try and relieve Tiberius.

00:23:12.670 --> 00:23:16.160 align:middle line:90%


00:23:16.160 --> 00:23:18.810 align:middle line:84%
The Crusaders dry
and tortuous route

00:23:18.810 --> 00:23:21.170 align:middle line:84%
would take them
past a landmark hill

00:23:21.170 --> 00:23:22.895 align:middle line:90%
called the Horns of Hattin.

00:23:22.895 --> 00:23:26.360 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:23:26.360 --> 00:23:39.250 align:middle line:90%


